snippet.title: Kingsman - The Secret Service Game Trailer
snippet.description:
Kingsman - The Secret Service Game

• Expand your armory by unlocking powerful and stylish weapons.
• Distinctive art style.
• Engaging stealth action-based gameplay.
• Narrative set in the Kingsman universe.
• Help Eggsy on an important mission to save Kingsman.

Download this narrative-driven spy game on your mobile device and start playing.

Download on iOS now - https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/kingsman-the-secret-service/id1272632812?ls=1&mt=8

Download from Googe Play now - https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.yesgnome.kingsmangame
